{
    "publish_date": "2011-06-08T19:04:57.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT9M37S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "If your life were a book", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you were the author,", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how would you want your story to go?", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s the question\nthat changed my life forever.", 
            "dur": "3.089", 
            "start": "14.573"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Growing up in a hot Last Vegas desert,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all I wanted was to be free.", 
            "dur": "2.322", 
            "start": "22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would daydream about\ntravelling the world,", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "living in a place where it snowed", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I would picture all of the stories", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I would go on to tell.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At the age of nineteen,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the day after I graduated high school,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "40"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I moved to a place where it snowed", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I became a massage therapist.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With this job all I needed were my hands", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and my massage table by my side", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I could go anywhere.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For the first time in my life,", 
            "dur": "2.755", 
            "start": "57.245"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt free, independent", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "60"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and completely in control of my life.", 
            "dur": "4.139", 
            "start": "63.525"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is until my life took a detour.", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "68.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went home from work early one day", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with what I thought was the flu", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and less than 24 hours later", 
            "dur": "2.435", 
            "start": "78.813"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was in a hospital", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on life support,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with less than a 2% chance of living.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It wasn&#39;t until days later", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as I lay in a coma", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that the doctors diagnosed me", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with bacterial meningitis,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a vaccine-preventable blood infection.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Over the course of two and a half months", 
            "dur": "2.385", 
            "start": "103.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I lost my spleen, my kidneys,", 
            "dur": "3.031", 
            "start": "105.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the hearing in my left ear", 
            "dur": "2.335", 
            "start": "109.665"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and both of my legs below the knee.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "112"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When my parents\nwheeled me out of the hospital", 
            "dur": "2.824", 
            "start": "117"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt like I had been\npieced back together", 
            "dur": "2.858", 
            "start": "119.824"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like a patchwork doll.", 
            "dur": "1.896", 
            "start": "122.682"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought the worst was over", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "until weeks later when I saw my new legs", 
            "dur": "2.393", 
            "start": "128.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the first time.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The calves were bulky blocks of metal", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with pipes bolted together for the ankles", 
            "dur": "2.928", 
            "start": "137.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a yellow rubber foot", 
            "dur": "2.016", 
            "start": "141.505"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the raised rubber line\nfrom the toe to the ankle", 
            "dur": "3.411", 
            "start": "144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to look like a vein.", 
            "dur": "2.589", 
            "start": "147.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t know what to expect", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "150"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I wasn&#39;t expecting that.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "153"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With my mum by my side", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and tears streaming down our faces", 
            "dur": "4.306", 
            "start": "159"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I strapped on these chunky legs", 
            "dur": "3.288", 
            "start": "164.712"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I stood up.", 
            "dur": "2.507", 
            "start": "168"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They were so painful and so confining", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "171"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that all I could think was", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "175"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how am I ever going to travel the world", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "178"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in these things?", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "180"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How was I ever going to live", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "182"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the life full of adventures and stories", 
            "dur": "2.728", 
            "start": "184"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as I always wanted?", 
            "dur": "2.272", 
            "start": "186.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And how was I going to snowboard again?", 
            "dur": "3.904", 
            "start": "189"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That day, I went home, I crawled into bed", 
            "dur": "3.175", 
            "start": "193.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this is what my life looked like", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the next few months.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "199"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Me passed out, escaping from reality", 
            "dur": "3.559", 
            "start": "201.441"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with my legs resting by my side.", 
            "dur": "3.822", 
            "start": "205.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was absolutely, physically\nand emotionally broken.", 
            "dur": "5.52", 
            "start": "210"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I knew that in order to move forward,", 
            "dur": "3.716", 
            "start": "218.284"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had to let go of the old Amy", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "222"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and learn to embrace the new Amy.", 
            "dur": "3.772", 
            "start": "227.228"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is when it dawned on me", 
            "dur": "2.614", 
            "start": "233.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I didn&#39;t have to be 5,5 ft. anymore.", 
            "dur": "2.654", 
            "start": "236.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could be as tall as I wanted!", 
            "dur": "2.302", 
            "start": "240.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "243"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or as short as I wanted\ndepending on who I was dating.", 
            "dur": "3.235", 
            "start": "248.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if I snowboarded again,", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my feet aren&#39;t going to get cold.", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "256.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.784", 
            "start": "258.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And best of all, I thought", 
            "dur": "1.786", 
            "start": "260.214"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can make my feet the size\nof all the shoes", 
            "dur": "3.247", 
            "start": "262.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that are on the sales rack\n(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.919", 
            "start": "265.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I did!", 
            "dur": "1.324", 
            "start": "268.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So there were benefits here.", 
            "dur": "2.41", 
            "start": "270.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was this moment that I asked myself", 
            "dur": "2.665", 
            "start": "273"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that life defining question:", 
            "dur": "2.335", 
            "start": "275.665"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if my life were a book", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "278.592"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I were the author,", 
            "dur": "2.578", 
            "start": "280.932"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how would I want the story to go?", 
            "dur": "2.359", 
            "start": "284.141"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I began to daydream.", 
            "dur": "2.058", 
            "start": "286.942"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I daydreamed like I did as a little girl", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I imagined myself", 
            "dur": "2.789", 
            "start": "292.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "walking gracefully,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "295"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "helping other people through my journey", 
            "dur": "2.441", 
            "start": "298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and snowboarding again.", 
            "dur": "2.559", 
            "start": "300.441"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I didn&#39;t just see myself", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "carving down a mountain of powder,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "305"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could actually feel it.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could feel the wind against my face", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "310"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the beat of my racing heart", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "313"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as if it were happening\nin that very moment.", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is when a new chapter\nin my life began.", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "321"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Four months later\nI was back up on a snowboard,", 
            "dur": "3.6", 
            "start": "327.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "although things didn&#39;t go\nquite as expected:", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "331"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my knees and my ankles wouldn&#39;t bend", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "333.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and at one point I traumatized\nall the skiers on the chair lift --", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)\nwhen I fell and my legs,", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "341"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "still attached to my snowboard --", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "344.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "347"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "went flying down the mountain --", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I was on top of the mountain still.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "354"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)\nI was so shocked,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was just as shocked as everybody else,\nand I was so discouraged,", 
            "dur": "3.958", 
            "start": "359"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I knew that if I could find\nthe right pair of feet", 
            "dur": "3.706", 
            "start": "363.294"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would be able to do this again.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "367"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is when I learned\nthat our borders", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "369"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and our obstacles\ncan only do two things:", 
            "dur": "2.798", 
            "start": "372"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one, stop us in our tracks", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or two, force us to get creative.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "379"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I did a year research,\nstill couldn&#39;t figure out", 
            "dur": "2.414", 
            "start": "383.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what kind of legs to use,", 
            "dur": "1.4", 
            "start": "385.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "couldn&#39;t find any resources\nthat could help me.", 
            "dur": "2.647", 
            "start": "387"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I decided to make a pair myself.", 
            "dur": "2.353", 
            "start": "389.647"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My leg maker and I\nput random parts together", 
            "dur": "3.071", 
            "start": "392.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we made a pair of feet\nthat I could snowboard in.", 
            "dur": "2.905", 
            "start": "395.637"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "399"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "rusted bolts, rubber,\nwood and neon pink duct tape.", 
            "dur": "4", 
            "start": "401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And yes, I can change my toe nail polish.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "408"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was these legs", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the best 21st birthday gift\nI could ever receive -", 
            "dur": "3.695", 
            "start": "413"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a new kidney from my dad -", 
            "dur": "2.757", 
            "start": "416.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that allowed me to follow my dreams again.", 
            "dur": "2.548", 
            "start": "419.452"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I started snowboarding,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "422"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then I went back to work,\nand back to school.", 
            "dur": "2.436", 
            "start": "424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then in 2005 I co-founded\na non-profit organization", 
            "dur": "3.439", 
            "start": "426.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for youth and young adults\nwith physical disabilities", 
            "dur": "2.977", 
            "start": "429.875"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so they could get involved\nwith action sports.", 
            "dur": "3.148", 
            "start": "432.852"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From there, I had the opportunity to go\nto South Africa", 
            "dur": "3.231", 
            "start": "436.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where I helped to put shoes\non thousands of children&#39;s feet", 
            "dur": "3.255", 
            "start": "440"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so they could attend school.", 
            "dur": "2.206", 
            "start": "443.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And just this past February,", 
            "dur": "2.179", 
            "start": "445.461"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I won two back to back\nWorld Cup gold medals -", 
            "dur": "4.239", 
            "start": "447.661"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "4.822", 
            "start": "452"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "- which made me", 
            "dur": "1.384", 
            "start": "461.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the highest ranked\nadaptive female snowboarder", 
            "dur": "2.923", 
            "start": "462.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the world.", 
            "dur": "1.867", 
            "start": "465.673"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "11 years ago, when I lost my legs,", 
            "dur": "3.241", 
            "start": "467.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had no idea what to expect.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you ask me today,", 
            "dur": "1.551", 
            "start": "474.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if I would ever want to\nchange my situation,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would have to say no.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because my legs haven&#39;t disabled me,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "481"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if anything they&#39;ve enabled me.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They forced me to rely on my imagination", 
            "dur": "3.46", 
            "start": "485.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and to believe in the possibilities,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "489"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s why I believe", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "492"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that our imaginations can be used as tools", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "493.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for breaking through borders", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because in our minds,\nwe can do anything", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we can be anything.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s believing in those dreams", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "504"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and facing our fears head on", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that allows us to live our lives", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "509"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "beyond our limits.", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "511"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And although today is about\ninnovation without borders,", 
            "dur": "3.396", 
            "start": "514.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have to say that in my life,", 
            "dur": "3.14", 
            "start": "517.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "innovation has only been possible", 
            "dur": "2.428", 
            "start": "521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because of my borders.", 
            "dur": "2.572", 
            "start": "523.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve learned that borders are where\nthe actual ends", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "526.585"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but also where the imagination", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "531"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the story begins.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "534"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the thought that\nI&#39;d like to challenge you with today", 
            "dur": "2.569", 
            "start": "536.927"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that maybe instead of\nlooking at our challenges and limitations", 
            "dur": "3.824", 
            "start": "540"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as something negative or bad,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "544"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we can begin to look at them as blessings,", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "547"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "magnificent gifts that can be used\nto ignite our imaginations", 
            "dur": "4.325", 
            "start": "550"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and help us go further\nthan we ever knew we could go.", 
            "dur": "3.749", 
            "start": "555.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not about breaking down borders.", 
            "dur": "3.973", 
            "start": "561.027"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s about pushing off of them", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "565"
        }, 
